title: Amazing Lease with Right to Purchase Opportunity
posting_body: ['Sign for a year Lease.', 'End it, or resign for up to five years.', 'Purchase at anytime OPTIONAL.', "*Pictures are a few of the real homes I've helped get tenants in*", "Call, email, or text me DETAILS on what you're looking for i.e beds, area, max monthly rental budget, house criteria etc.", 'Contact me to learn more about an innovative Rental with Option to Purchase program.', 'Unlike rent to own programs or other lease options, there is no obligation to buy and no non-refundable option fees.', 'Rentals start around $1,950.00', 'Basic Requirements to Qualify:', '• Annual household income of $65,000+', '• Stable employment', '• No history of eviction or other landlord issues', '• No pending bankruptcy', '• 580 FICO Credit score', 'Andre Jones', 'Real Estate Broker', 'Skyline Properties Inc']
